00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
[Intro music]

00:06.000 --> 00:16.000
Memories of you still stay with me, tightly held like something I can’t let go.

00:16.000 --> 00:26.000
Even silence feels heavy now, your thoughts keep coming back again and again.

00:26.000 --> 00:36.000
This loneliness is harsh, it doesn’t let me live in peace.

00:36.000 --> 00:46.000
I keep you in my songs, holding those memories close to my heart.

00:46.000 --> 00:56.000
Wherever I go, I keep finding traces of you waiting there.

00:56.000 --> 01:06.000
I’ve kept everything safe that reminds me of you, like it’s all I have left.

01:06.000 --> 01:16.000
Life feels dark without you, nothing seems right anymore.

01:16.000 --> 01:26.000
I pray just to be free from this pain and these endless breaths.

01:26.000 --> 01:36.000
If you ever remember me, just call once and I’d come running back.

01:36.000 --> 01:46.000
I would break every rule of the world just to keep your love.

01:46.000 --> 01:56.000
You made me emotional, you turned my feelings into words and songs.

01:56.000 --> 02:06.000
This separation has slowly broken me down from inside.

02:06.000 --> 02:16.000
Still, I keep every promise I made to you, holding onto them.

02:16.000 --> 02:26.000
My whole life feels like it was dedicated only to you.

02:26.000 --> 02:30.000
[Outro fades]
